strings: <se_def>China: Why wouldn't it be!! Some require a little effort in the right direction.
<se_high>Accuracy: You're not a Templar, are you? Some people might think that dressing like a goddess is against the rules.
<se_def>China: And this is very good! The gods do not care about such nonsense!
<se_high>Accuracy: Don't cry for me if the Goddess makes you fall from the mountain!
